# Files the `tauri dev` watcher should ignore (gitignore syntax).
#
# Compiled COB output: the anim plugin writes `<name>.cob` next to the `.bos`
# being compiled. When that source lives inside a watched crate (e.g. the
# anim crate's test fixtures), the new `.cob` would otherwise trigger a dev
# rebuild + app restart. Compiler output is never a build input, so ignore it.
*.cob
